indications_original: Se-Natal 19 Chewable Tablets are indicated for use in improving the nutritional status of women throughout pregnancy and in the postnatal period for both lactating and non-lactating mothers. Se-Natal 19 Chewable Tablets are also useful in improving the nutritional status of women prior to conception.
contraindications_original: One tablet daily, or as directed by a physician.
warningsAndPrecautions_original:
Se-Natal 19 Chewable Tablets for oral administration are supplied as multi-color-speckled, round tablets debossed "TL015," packaged in bottles of 100 tablets.
                  
                     Product Code: 13925-117-01
adverseReactions_original: This product is contraindicated in patients with a known hypersensitivity to any of the ingredients.
